# 子任务 [/subtask]

## 创建子任务 [POST /subtask]
+ Parameters
    + s_token: `owenxin2ns123nasdfnqj8dnqoi`(string , required) - 账号会话token
    + task_id: `201301` (number, required) - 父任务ID 或者 父任务临时ID
    + content: `第一步完成xxx的调研`(string, required) - 子任务内容

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        + message:`ok` (string) - 响应正常
        + subtask_id:`28` (number) - 子任务ID

## 删除子任务 [DELETE /subtask]
+ Parameters
    + s_token: `owenxin2ns123nasdfnqj8dnqoi`(string , required) - 账号会话token
    + task_id: `1j2joawjj9203=`(string, required) - 任务ID
    + subtask_id: `23`(string, required) - 子任务ID
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        + message:`ok` (string) - 响应正常